title: WakuWaku
typeOfFood: Ovo, Organic, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service wok restaurant. Food is prepared in a wok with many dishes can be made vegan by request. Also offers salad, soup, and tortilla. The interior is made from recyclable materials. Relocated from Schauenburgerstr. 55-57 in 2014. Reported still operating as of Jan 2016.
